	description: "[
				 Access to a .ini style configuration file. Comment
				 character settable; defaults to ';'. Category items
				 take the form '[xxxx]'. Name/value pair entries 
				 take the form:
				 	name = value
				 any whitespace can occur around the '='
				 ]"
